diting related to a current interaction with you and concurrent transactions, including, but not limited to, counting ad impressions to unique visitors, verifying positioning and quality of ad impressions, and auditing compliance; short-term, transient use, including, but not limited to, the contextual customization of ads shown as part of the same interaction; detecting security incidents, protecting against malicious, deceptive, fraudulent, or illegal activity, and prosecuting those responsible for that activity; debugging to identify and repair errors that impair existing intended functionality; undertaking internal research for technological development and demonstration; and undertaking activities to verify or maintain the quality or safety of a service that is owned or controlled by us, and to improve, upgrade, or enhance the service that is owned or controlled by us. We may share or disclose all of the above categories of information with service partners that assist with our internal functions, such as analyzing data, maintain the security of our systems, ensuring our compliance with the law. We may also share the above information with our affiliates (e.g., Movefast Company Co. Ltd., Belogical Pte. Ltd.) in order to better serve you or maintain our business Category of Personal Information Recipient Categories Identifiers Our affiliated companies, solution provider, partners, system management and operation service provider Commercial Information Solution provider, system management and operation service provider Geolocation Data Solution provider, system management and operation service provider Internet and Other Electronic Network Activity Information Our affiliated companies, partners, solution provider, system management and operation service provider Audio, Electronic, Visual, or Similar Information Solution provider, system management and operation service provider Inferences Solution provider, system management and operation service provider Sold th