ave the right to request that we delete the personal information we have collected from you. You also have the right to opt out of the sale of your personal information by clicking here: Do Not Sell My Information. Additionally, you have the right to not be discriminated against as a result of exercising these rights. You or your authorized agents may submit an access or deletion request, by clicking here or by contacting us as specified in the “Contact Us” section of this Privacy Policy. In order for us to honor a request made by your agent, you must submit proof of your written authorization of the agent. To help protect your privacy and maintain security, we take steps to verify your identity before granting you access to your personal information or complying with your request. If you have an account with us, we may verify your identity by requiring you to sign into your account. To the extent permitted by applicable law, we may charge a reasonable fee to comply with your request.